The perspective is from a low angle, looking upwards towards the towering buildings and the clear blue sky. The sun shines brightly in the top right corner of the image, casting a warm glow over the scene. The street itself is lined with lush green trees and bushes, adding a touch of nature to the urban landscape. The buildings, painted in shades of beige and brown, rise majestically on either side of the street, their windows reflecting the sunlight. The overall color palette of the image is dominated by shades of green, blue, and beige, creating a harmonious blend of natural and man-made elements.
